The Western Lotto Nigeria Limited has diversified into the online gaming business by launching a new brand, Lotto9ja. At a briefing in Lagos, the General Manager, Western Lotto/Lotto9ja, Tajudeen Usman said the launch of the new gaming brand is being driven by the same enthusiam that that prodded the launch of Western Bet, a sister company few years ago. According to the General Manager, the new gaming brand would be largely driven by internet and technology. He added that Lotto9ja will leverage on lessons learnt and consolidate on gains made. He was however quick to warn fraudsters not to fake the gaming brand, saying the company already has every proprietary rights on it. He expressed hope that since Nigeria is a country govern by law, the long arm of law will no doubt bring such persons to book.  Automotive industry: Transformation unfolds in Nigeria UAC Foods appoints Chidi Okoro as new MD p28 business Dear Esteemed reader, As part of our drive to keep improving the content of our newspaper, we are conducting a readership survey to enable us serve you better. Kindly take two minutes of your time to fill in this questionnaire. Thank you for your time. Click here to begin